Frequently Asked Questions

Quick answers to common questions

What's your typical project timeline?

Project timelines vary based on scope and complexity. Simple logo designs typically take 1-2 weeks, while complete brand identity projects can take 4-6 weeks. We'll provide a detailed timeline during our initial consultation.

Do you work with small businesses?

We work with businesses of all sizes, from startups to established enterprises. We offer flexible packages and solutions that can fit various budgets and requirements.

What's included in your partnership with Galadevs?

Our partnership allows us to offer complete digital solutions including web development, software development, UI/UX design, and prototyping. You get design and development expertise under one roof.

How do you handle revisions?

We include multiple revision rounds in all our packages. We work closely with you throughout the process to ensure the final result exceeds your expectations and aligns perfectly with your vision.
